dialogue.introduction: The eighth ship of Kagerou-class destroyer, I'm Yukikaze. I'll be in your care!
dialogue.library_intro: I'm Yukikaze, eighth ship of the Kagerou-class destroyer. Among the destroyers of the main fleet, while taking part in over 10 major naval battles, I'm the only one to have survived the war with barely any damage. Miracle destroyer? Nope, it was no miracle!
dialogue.secretary3: Um, do you have any business with Yukikaze?
dialogue.wedding: The miracle destroyer... no, that's not it. It's only because I always wanna stay by the commander... Oh, wait, I mean, t-that's not it either!
dialogue.equipment2: I can feel the kiss of the fortune goddess!
dialogue.supply: I can feel the kiss of the fortune goddess!
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: Repairing so I can rejoin operations!
dialogue.docking_complete: The docked ship has finished repairs!
dialogue.ship_construction: A new comrade has been launched!
dialogue.mvp: Yukikaze, came back alive as always! Thanks, commander.
dialogue.minor_damaged1: The "unsinkable" title is not only for show!!
dialogue.moderately_damaged: Uhh, but, I- I won't sink, okay.
dialogue.sunk: The unsinkable ship...does not exist in this world.
dialogue.second_anniversary_2015: Commander! It's an anniversary right? Congratulations! Yukikaze's happy too!
dialogue.rainy_season_2015: Commander! There are a lot of rainy days recently. It's quite annoying since our uniforms and laundries won't dry as well, right?
dialogue.fall_event_2015: Member of the 2nd torpedo squad, Kagerou model Yukikaze reporting for duty.
dialogue.christmas_2015: Commander~! It's Christmas! The cake and food is delicious! Commander~! Eat, eat!
dialogue.end_of_year_2015: Commander! This year has ended as well. Yukikaze will clean the room too, yes!
dialogue.new_year_2016: Happy New Year, Commander! Please treat me and the torpedo squadron well this year too!
